These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-1::.
House: futuristic, modern, art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman, colonial
City: san-francisco, nizza, new-york, marseilles, miami, colone
 1. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
 3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the craftsman house and the person traveling to nizza##2
 5. the person traveling to miami is the art-deco house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 7. the person traveling to nizza is the modern house##1
 8. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 9. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
10. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
11. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4    |    5     |  6   |
| House      | art-deco | ranch-style   | craftsman | futuristic | modern    | colonial  |
| City   | miami  | marseilles | colone   | san-francisco  | nizza | new-york |

