.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, pall-mall, bongani, dannemann, dunhill, montecristo
City: miami, nizza, hannover, colone, prague, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 4. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to hannover is the bongani-smoker##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
11. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
12. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
13. the dunhill-smoker is the person traveling to miami##1
14. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
15. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
16. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | montecristo | bongani | vegafina         | pall-mall | dannemann |
| City   | miami    | prague      | hannover      | colone | nizza   | hamburg |

