.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, sailing, swimming, basketball, skiing
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, orange, ivory, purple, yellow, pink
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 9. the person who likes ivory is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who likes pink##2
10. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Sport      | skiing | cricket | basketball   | swimming | snowboarding   | sailing |
| Color   | orange    | ivory         | pink | yellow     | red | purple     |

