.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, blue, turtle, black, ebony, emerald
6 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, horse, goat, fish, dog
 1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
 2. the person who likes turtle is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who likes coral##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
 7. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turtle##5
 8. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
11. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
13. the person who likes turtle is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| Color   | coral     | blue     | turtle  | emerald     | black | ebony |
| Pet       | rabbit | dog | horse | turtle | goat          | fish   |

