 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
 4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who likes amber is the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
10. the person who likes yellow is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet   | mouse | bird     | guinea-pig    | lizard | hamster | hedgehog    |
| Color         | amber  | lavender | purple | ivory     | brown | yellow |

