The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, september, march, april, december, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
10. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
11. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |       4       |    5    |       6       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | scientific  | disaster | documentary     | superhero | satire        |
| Birthday         | june | december | march    | april | september  | january |

