 1. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 5. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the dog##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
10. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
11. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
12. the owner of the frog is the person who likes azure##1
13. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Pet   | snake  | dog        | lizard  | pony     | frog | turtle |
| Color       | blood-red | ivory | red | emerald | azure  | aquamarine          |

