.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, comedy, animation, horror, drama, family
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, july, october, january, february, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 9. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Movie-Genre         | family    | horror | comedy   | animation | mystery    | drama |
| Birthday   | june | september  | february | october      | january | july    |

 